{"tid":945201,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【人住公屋我住公屋】曾鈺成梁國雄再把臂同遊　黃秋生住法國公屋","createTime":"2018-12-17T16:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T06:23:42.000Z","uid":141060,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"50474b735d77a6fbac7c2d40b9ffa9c8acd0d989","tid":945201,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:30:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://viu.tv/encore/where-you-live/where-you-livee1chang-yuk-sing-leung-gwok-hung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fviu.tv%2Fencore%2Fwhere-you-live%2Fwhere-you-livee1chang-yuk-sing-leung-gwok-hung&d=whdR2Uabg5GS9qNvSfZupgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=5bf8438e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://viu.tv/encore/where-you-live/where-you-livee1chang-yuk-sing-leung-gwok-hung</a><br />\n<br />\n由曾鈺成、梁國雄、黃秋生、林一峰、林二汶及盤菜瑩子擔任嘉賓主持的ViuTV節目《人住公屋 我住公屋》昨日（14/12）在公屋大排檔舉行發布會。<br />\n<br />\n節目中，一班嘉賓主持不但會入住世界各地最有代表性的公屋，更會與當地居民打交道，感受異國公屋的地道生活。發布會上，到日本參觀「團地」的盤菜瑩子分享了當地公屋設計風格及申請程序。而一同到訪西班牙及奧地利的林一峰和林二汶，便比較了兩地公屋及自小長大的香港公屋坪石邨。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡一向被指與香港環境相似，把臂到當地參觀「組屋」的曾鈺成、梁國雄分享二人對兩地公屋異同的見解，又分享新加坡公屋環境值得香港借鏡的地方。最後，到丹麥及法國拍攝的黃秋生分享了對當地公屋的觀感，又透露自己會選擇丹麥、法國或香港的公屋居住。"},{"pid":"9bf00c2a1f6729a6aa5384592486e7e023893bdc","tid":945201,"uid":141060,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:31:25.000Z","msg":"嘩 屌你老味...第一集已經睇到扯晒火  同香港差十萬八千里<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a9b54678454f5cc4954c248e6921a80a7fa6bd","tid":945201,"uid":225871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:36:13.000Z","msg":"好似幾正咁"},{"pid":"c1bc3aa2630c6e9bba6fade63c78229b1a513cc6","tid":945201,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-1